# API token for monitoring and fleet schedule API (D2.5 Bearer)
# Managed by: sudo dsign-api-token install | rotate | show | status
# File on player: /etc/dsign/api.env (not in git)
# Fleet runbook: docs/D2_OPS_FLEET.md
#
# Health:
# curl -s -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/health | jq .
#
# Schedule (no CSRF with Bearer):
# curl -s -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/schedule/rules | jq .
#
# DSIGN_API_TOKEN=
